Scratch 2.0 Plug-in for Leap Motion

This program lets you connect a Leap Motion to Scratch 2.0. It sends data for up to two hands and ten fingers.

Download in Leap Motion Airspace store:
https://airspace.leapmotion.com/apps/scratch-2-0-plug-in-for-leap-motion/windows

Downoad on Scratch forums (Linux):
http://scratch.mit.edu/discuss/topic/12405/

Example Projects:
http://scratch.mit.edu/studios/236466/

